explanation: [0-0] Three dancers stand in a room with wooden floors, a white sofa, white walls, and gray curtains. A ceiling fan hangs above. The woman in the middle wears a white tank top and blue floral pants. She is flanked by two men. The man on the left wears a white shirt and green pants, while the man on the right wears a green shirt and grayish-white jeans. They hold one arm raised in front of them.

[0-10] They lower their arms together. The woman turns her head, raises both hands, and looks at the man on the left. The two men look at her simultaneously, the man on the right with his hand on his hip. Then, the woman smiles and raises both hands, pointing her index fingers at her temples. Next, she spreads her arms and performs a noble courtesy to the front. After that, she steps back behind the two men, hands on her hips. The two men walk forward in sync, get into a horse stance, bend over, and start shaking their heads. Afterward, they straighten up, turn their bodies to the right, and look forward together, dancing energetic steps. The woman behind them follows their steps.
